---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Arclet Copier">
    <Header lang="en" />

    <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-soft-lg p-8 md:p-12">
                <h1
                    class="text-4xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-8"
                >
                    Privacy Policy
                </h1>

                <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                    <p class="text-secondary-600 mb-8">
                        Last updated: September 19, 2025
                    </p>

                    <section class="mb-8">
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4"
                        >
                            1. Information Collection
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700 mb-4">
                            Arclet Copier is a browser extension, and we are
                            committed to protecting your privacy. We do not
                            collect, store, or transmit your personal
                            information.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-secondary-700 space-y-2">
                            <li>
                                We do not collect your personal identification
                                information
                            </li>
                            <li>We do not track your browsing behavior</li>
                            <li>We do not collect the content you copy</li>
                            <li>We do not share any data with third parties</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-8">
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4"
                        >
                            2. Local Storage
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700 mb-4">
                            The extension may store some configuration
                            information locally on your device, including:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-secondary-700 space-y-2">
                            <li>User settings and preferences</li>
                            <li>Extension configuration</li>
                            <li>
                                Copy history (stored locally only, not uploaded)
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-4">
                            This information is stored only on your local device
                            and is not sent to our servers or any third-party
                            services.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-8">
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4"
                        >
                            3. Permission Usage
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700 mb-4">
                            The extension requires certain browser permissions
                            to function properly:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-secondary-700 space-y-2">
                            <li>
                                <strong>activeTab</strong>: Access the current
                                active tab to perform copy functions
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <strong>storage</strong>: Store user settings
                                locally
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <strong>clipboardWrite</strong>: Write content
                                to the clipboard
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-4">
                            We only use these permissions when necessary and do
                            not abuse or exceed the scope required for
                            functionality.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-8">
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4"
                        >
                            4. Third-Party Services
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700">
                            We do not use any third-party analytics services,
                            advertising services, or data collection services.
                            The extension runs entirely locally and does not
                            send any data to external servers.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-8">
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4"
                        >
                            5. Data Security
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700">
                            Since we do not collect or store your personal data,
                            there is no risk of data breaches. All functionality
                            runs on your local device, ensuring maximum privacy
                            protection.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-8">
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4"
                        >
                            6. Policy Updates
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700">
                            We may update this privacy policy from time to time.
                            Any changes will be posted on this page and users
                            will be notified when the extension is updated.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4"
                        >
                            7. Contact Us
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-secondary-700">
                            If you have any questions or concerns about this
                            privacy policy, please contact us through our GitHub
                            project page:
                            <a
                                href="https://github.com/rokcso/arclet-copier"
                                class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 underline"
                                target="_blank"
                            >
                                https://github.com/rokcso/arclet-copier
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>
